# vrvish Brand Guidelines

Brand documentation can be found (and should be stored) here: `C:\GitHub\T1-vrvish-core\organisation\brand\`. It holds the definitive brand identity, visual assets, and typography for the overall Vrvish ecosystem (including `vrvish.com`).

## Brand Folder Structure

```
organisation/brand/
├── outputs/           # Production-ready assets (use these)
│   ├── humain/        # humain.svg
│   ├── logo/          # vrvish_3vs_white.svg, vrvish_3vs_no_white.svg
│   └── type/vrvishSans/ — font glyphs (i.svg, j.svg)
└── working/           # Source files, edits
    ├── humain/
    ├── logo/
    ├── type/vrvishSans/
    └── SS/            # Source SVGs, Inkscape exports
```

Assets are synced from `outputs/` to CommandHub and marketing site via `scripts/T2-tools/Sync-BrandAssets.ps1`.

